data.description: Newer stilt island-style home with water views from the covered upstairs balcony and living room. 3 bedroom 2 bath - the perfect second home, short-term rental investment or experience the coastal lifestyle 24/7 as a full-timer. Only 5 minutes away from the nearest boat ramp and 10 minutes away from Rockport and Aransas Pass. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout; all countertops are quartz. The main bedroom is en suite. Plenty of room in the 700sf garage with 10x10 garage door to park a boat and store all your fishing equipment and then some.   Need more outdoor space?  Enjoy 1000sf of additional covered carport - maybe a downstairs chillin' spot, or create an outdoor kitchen. Rinse off after a day on the water with your outdoor shower (hot & cold water). 50 amp service has been when the home  was built for an RV hookup.
